Title: Toxic Infestation
Description:
The Healing Wings need access to our support creche, but it's still overflowing with an infestation of toxic beetles.

I'm sure Viridia would appreciate it if we helped exterminate those pests.
ObjectivesText: Kill beetles in the Caldera of the Menders.
PortraitGiverText: This overgrown species of beetle is infused with the toxins plaguing the Support Creche.
